data.description: Don't Miss Out on This Beautiful Summerhill Model Home in Cedar Ridge Estates Lake Villa! This Home Sit's on an Oversized Lot & Boasts 4 Beds + an Office, 2.5 Baths, Vaulted Ceilings, Formal Living & Dining Room, Large Family Room w/ Fireplace. Open Concept Kitchen w/ Separate Light Filled Breakfast Area, a Bonus Room That Can be Used for an Office, Playroom or Additional 5th Bedroom, Separate Main Floor Laundry Room off of an Attached 3 Car Garage! Upstairs There is All New Vinyl Wood Flooring, 4 Bedrooms & 2 Additional Full Baths. The Primary is MASSIVE with a Large En Suite that has a Walk-in Closet, Jacuzzi Tub and Separate Shower. Dual HVAC Systems, Extremely Large Unfinished DRY Basement, Just Waiting for Your Ideas! Outside Features a Newer Roof, Solar Panels & an Automated Lawn Sprinkler System to Make Your Lawn Maintenace a Breeze! Nothing to do but Move In & Enjoy this Picture-Perfect Home.
